Class CreateExaminationController

  • java.lang.Object
    • client.control.CreateExaminationController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IController, Initializable

    public class CreateExaminationController
extends Object
implements IController, Initializable
    CreateExaminationController handle the Examinations by the lab worker from specific reference that the specialist gave the Client , The LabWorker can add pictures and comments to the examination.
    Author:
    Raz
